  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of Sofpironium Bromide in Subjects With Axillary Hyperhidrosis (BBI-4000-CL-301)</brief_title>
  <acronym>Cardigan I</acronym>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Blinded, Vehicle-Controlled Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Topically Applied Sofpironium Bromide Gel, 15% in Subjects With Axillary Hyperhidrosis</official_title>
